      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once dissolved, add your <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>red chilli relish</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>peanut sauce</strong></p>",
